{"id":308264,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-上海维权人士举办第7期免费法律知识学习/","date":"2013-08-10T03:48:28Z","modified":"2013-08-10T03:48:28Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士举办第7期免费法律知识学习讲座（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>日 中午<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span></span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>分～<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span></span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>分，上海公民免</span><span>费学习</span><span>法律知</span><span>识</span><span>，推</span><span>动</span><span>依法治</span><span>国</span><span>第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>课</span><span>成功完成。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本期有<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>位公民冒着近<span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span>℃高</span><span>温坚</span><span>持</span><span>参</span><span>加</span><span>学习</span><span>法律。大家希望中</span><span>国</span><span>早日成</span><span>为</span><span>法治</span><span>国</span><span>家，</span><span>愿更多的人</span><span>参</span><span>加</span><span>学习</span><span>，推</span><span>动</span><span>依法治</span><span>国</span><span>人人有</span><span>责</span><span>任和</span><span>义务</span><span>。只要</span><span>你</span><span>愿意</span><span>参</span><span>加</span><span>学习</span><span>，无</span><span>论你</span><span>是官</span><span>员</span><span>或者百姓，一律平等享受免</span><span>费</span><span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本期主</span><span>讲</span><span>人是上海法律工作者</span><span>顾国</span><span>平老</span><span>师</span><span>，主</span><span>讲</span><span>的</span><span>题</span><span>目是《行政</span><span>诉讼</span><span>法》要点之</span><span>四<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>顾国</span><span>平老</span><span>师</span><span>的</span><span>讲课内</span><span>容如下：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>《行政</span><span>诉讼</span><span>法》</span><span>第六十二</span><span>条</span><span>：“</span><span>当</span><span>事人</span><span>对</span><span>已</span><span>经发</span><span>生法律效力的判</span><span>决</span><span>、裁</span><span>定，</span><span>认为</span><span>确有</span><span>错误</span><span>的，可以向原</span><span>审</span><span>人民法院或者上一</span><span>级</span><span>人民法院提出申</span><span>诉</span><span>，但判</span><span>决</span><span>、裁定不停止</span><span>执</span><span>行</span><span>。”<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>可是，我</span><span>们维权</span><span>的上</span><span>访</span><span>一族人，</span><span>绝</span><span>大多</span><span>数</span><span>都遭遇到</span><span>这种</span><span>不公正的</span><span>对</span><span>待。</span><span>而且存在的</span><span>错误</span><span>相</span><span>当</span><span>明</span><span>显</span><span>和</span><span>严</span><span>重，有些</span><span>还</span><span>存在着</span><span>严</span><span>重的侵</span><span>权</span><span>犯罪行</span><span>为</span><span>。但，</span><span>我</span><span>们</span><span>向上</span><span>级</span><span>法院，甚至去北京</span><span>向最高</span><span>层</span><span>申</span><span>诉</span><span>反映都少有</span><span>给</span><span>予</span><span>纠</span><span>正解</span><span>决</span><span>的，因此，</span><span>这条规</span><span>定</span><span>虽</span><span>定好，但在</span><span>现实</span><span>社</span><span>会当</span><span>中却非常少</span><span>见</span><span>。特</span><span>别</span><span>是行政案件，至少我</span><span>们没</span><span>有遇到</span><span>过</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>《行政</span><span>诉讼</span><span>法》</span><span>第六十四</span><span>条</span><span>：“人民</span><span>检</span><span>察院</span><span>对</span><span>人民法院已</span><span>经发</span><span>生法律效力的判</span><span>决</span><span>、裁定，</span><span>发现违</span><span>反法律、法</span><span>规规</span><span>定的，有</span><span>权</span><span>按照</span><span>审</span><span>判</span><span>监</span><span>督程序提出抗</span><span>诉</span><span>。</span><span>”<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>但是，在整</span><span>个</span><span>司法</span><span>实践</span><span>中，我</span><span>们</span><span>基本</span><span>没</span><span>看到</span><span>这条规</span><span>定在</span><span>现实</span><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>所</span><span>产</span><span>生的作用的存在，</span><span>并没</span><span>有看到公、</span><span>检</span><span>、法、司之</span><span>间</span><span>，能相互</span><span>独</span><span>立、</span><span>监</span><span>督、制</span><span>约</span><span>。因此，</span><span>这条规</span><span>定也是</span><span>形同</span><span>虚设</span><span>，只是</span><span>个摆设</span><span>，只是</span><span>给</span><span>外</span><span>国</span><span>人看</span><span>热闹</span><span>用的。</span><span>没</span><span>有一点</span><span>现实</span><span>意</span><span>义</span><span>，是</span><span>为</span><span>了根据需要而用的，不是</span><span>为</span><span>了</span><span>纠错</span><span>的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>《行政</span><span>诉讼</span><span>法》</span><span>第六十七</span><span>条</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>“公民、法人或者其他</span><span>组织</span><span>的合法</span><span>权</span><span>益受到行政机</span><span>关</span><span>或者行政机</span><span>关</span><span>工作人</span><span>员</span><span>作出的具体行政行</span><span>为</span><span>侵犯造成</span><span>损</span><span>害的，有</span><span>权请</span><span>求</span><span>赔偿</span><span>。</span><span>公民、法人或者其他</span><span>组织单独</span><span>就</span><span>损</span><span>害</span><span>赔偿</span><span>提出</span><span>请</span><span>求，</span><span>应当</span><span>先由行政机</span><span>关</span><span>解</span><span>决</span><span>。</span><span>对</span><span>行政机</span><span>关</span><span>的</span><span>处</span><span>理不服，可以向人民法院提起</span><span>诉讼</span><span>。</span><span>赔偿诉讼</span><span>可以适用</span><span>调</span><span>解。</span><span>”<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>可是，</span><span>现实</span><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>中</span><span>，普通公民遇到行政机</span><span>关</span><span>或者其工作人</span><span>员</span><span>不法侵害</span><span>时</span><span>，根本就</span><span>没办</span><span>法去抵制不法侵害。</span><span>至于</span><span>赔偿</span><span>之事，</span><span>真</span><span>是天方夜</span><span>谭</span><span>，根本</span><span>没</span><span>有可能性。首先，法院可以</span><span>违</span><span>法不立案。然后，</span><span>骗你</span><span>去信</span><span>访</span><span>。而信</span><span>访</span><span>部</span><span>门</span><span>是一</span><span>个</span><span>地地道道的皮球公司，把公民上</span><span>访</span><span>的冤情</span><span>来来</span><span>回回</span><span>、上上下下、</span><span>转来转</span><span>去的，</span><span>踢</span><span>皮球似地</span><span>拖着不</span><span>办</span><span>。直到把</span><span>你</span><span>拖</span><span>长</span><span>、拖久、拖</span><span>垮</span><span>、拖累、拖死</span><span>为</span><span>止</span><span>。因</span><span>为</span><span>事情跟着人走的，人死了，事情也了掉了。所以</span><span>，上述</span><span>条</span><span>款</span><span>，好像是天空中的星星和月亮——可望不可取。因此，</span><span>当</span><span>今中</span><span>国</span><span>的民</span><span>众实</span><span>在是</span><span>多灾多</span><span>难啊</span><span>！</span><span>维权</span><span>的上</span><span>访</span><span>族</span><span>诉</span><span>控无</span><span>门</span><span>。</span><span>所</span><span>谓</span><span>行政</span><span>赔偿</span><span>，比登天</span><span>还难</span><span>。</span><span>到</span><span>处</span><span>是</span><span>踢</span><span>皮球式的</span><span>转来转</span><span>去，官官相</span><span>护</span><span>，</span><span>没</span><span>有具体</span><span>的方案</span><span>给</span><span>人。更加可</span><span>恶</span><span>、可恨、可怕的事是：</span><span>只要</span><span>你</span><span>走上申</span><span>诉</span><span>、控告或者</span><span>检举</span><span>的道路，就</span><span>会</span><span>招</span><span>来压</span><span>制和打</span><span>击报复</span><span>。</span><span>要把</span><span>你</span><span>拘留、</span><span>劳教</span><span>、判刑、</span><span>关</span><span>黑</span><span>监狱</span><span>、</span><span>送精神病院、强迫失踪、任意</span><span>羁</span><span>押、株</span><span>连</span><span>九族、</span><span>暴力</span><span>殴</span><span>打致</span><span>伤</span><span>致死</span><span>，使上</span><span>访维权</span><span>人士在有冤的基</span><span>础</span><span>上——冤上加冤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" t